f XML</strong></p>   <div class="example-contents"><p>     It is possible to directly output XML by using the     <a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/wrappers.php.php#wrappers.php.output" class="link">php://output stream wrapper</a>.   </p></div>   <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$out </span><span style="color: #007700">=new </span><span style="color: #9876AA">XMLWriter</span><span style="color: #007700">();<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$out</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">openURI</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'php://output'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></span></div>   </div>  </div> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 notes" id="refsect1-xmlwriter.openuri-notes">  <h3 class="title">注释</h3>  <blockquote class="note" style="border:1px gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">注意</strong>:    <p class="para">    On Windows, files opened with this function are locked until the writer is    released.   </p>  </p></blockquote> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-xmlwriter.openuri-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link XMLWriter::openMemory()} - Create new xmlwriter using memory for string output</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
     * @return bool Object oriented style: Returns <b>TRUE</b> on success or <b>FALSE</b> on failure.*/
